	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p>To <addressee>Miss E. Bomeisler</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Secy. Ladies&#39; <add>&#63;</add> Home Association.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dr Madam.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">It would afford me great pleasure to com&#45;<lb/>ply with the request of the society you represent<lb/> to address them on <date>Tuesday the 12<hi rend="sup">th</hi> of February</date><lb/> next&#44; if it were in my power.  But there is one<lb/> clause in the <add>&#63;</add> &#8220;at the Portuguese Synagogue&#8221;<lb/> which is a ban to my compliance&#59; as the cir&#45;<lb/>cumstances which attended my connection<lb/> with the body <sic>worshipping</sic> therein would <del>make</del><lb/> evidently render it unbecoming for my <del>part</del> to<lb/> take part in any celebration or meeting held<lb/> in a building over which the president&#44; <add>&#63;</add><lb/> and members of the Portuguese congregation claim<lb/> and have the exclusive control.  There is how&#45;<lb/>ever the condition which if complied with will<lb/> enable me to do so as I am requested&#44; that is<lb/> if a notice from the President and Adjuntor<add>&#63;</add><lb/> or of a majority of them at least were sent to<lb/> me that my addressing a public body like yours<lb/> has the full approbation&#44; consent and is in accordance</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>with the wishes of the gentlemen referred to in<lb/> their official capacity.  There is ample<lb/> time yet to obtain this consent in writing before<lb/> the <date>12<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date> proximo&#59; and if not&#44; or if <del>not&#44; or if this assert<add>&#63;</add></del> it<lb/> cannot be obtained in a form and manner<lb/> recognized by me&#44; there will be full opportunity<lb/> to select some person in my place who has<lb/> no such reason to refuse reluctantly com&#45;<lb/>pliance&#44; as I am compelled to do.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Have the goodness to inform me at your<lb/> earliest convenience of the determination<lb/> of your board&#44; and accept in the mean&#45;<lb/>while the assurance of my high regard.</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)"><persName role="author">Isaac Leeser</persName></p>
				<p><placeName>371 Walnut St</placeName></p>
				<p><date>January 24<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5616</date>.</p>
		</body>
